title: [LFM] Silver/Gold LF Jungler
body:
Silver/Gold casual team looking for a reliable jungler, 
must be willing to play some norms with us to test our compatibility.
We play daily sometime between 9pm-12am (UTC +12)  

We use Razer comms for our VoIP and is preferred that our jungler can use with us too, http://www.razerzone.com/comms

Leave your Summoner name and your top 3 preferred junglers if interested :)

replies.body: Im a jungle main, gold v. Can play heaps of heaps of tank/devourer/ad/ap junglers
Jungle Main, I main Shyvana at the moment but can pick heavy cc junglers such as sej/gragas/skarner etc. I am Plat 3 and my IGN if you want to add me is Vi So Mad ^^
